text: Besian Çeliku (born 18 July 1987, in Tiranë) is an Albanian football player. ==Club career== Having started his career with KF Tirana, he was loaned out to Kastrioti Krujë, Përparimi Kukës and Skënderbeu Korçë before moving to KS Lushnja.Soccerway profile He was also a member of the Albania U17 and U21 national teams.Albania U21 ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Footballers from Tirana Category:Albanian footballers Category:Association football central defenders Category:Albania youth international footballers Category:Albania under-21 international footballers Category:KF Tirana players Category:KS Kastrioti players Category:FK Kukësi players Category:KF Skënderbeu Korçë players Category:KS Lushnja players
